The claim with the title 'PoliGraph: Klobuchar right on student debt, jobs ' says Sen. Amy Klobuchar stopped by the MPR News State Fair booth this week to talk about beer , guns and the economy. But her answer to a question about student loan debt stood out to PoliGraph. “ when you look at the average debt for students in Minnesota … it’s something like $30,000, ” Klobuchar said. College graduates areN’t trained for the jobs that are available, she added. “ one of the things that i’ve found frustrating is that we have something like 80 percent of our manufacturers in Minnesota have job openings, ” she said. 
